<ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">NIS-3</ENAMEX> sponsor) specifically to refine the NIS-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX> design. Together with the rest
of the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">conferees</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Besharov</ENAMEX> recommended no changes in the NIS methodology and
