<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Dembosky</ENAMEX> characterized the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1.4 million</NUMEX> additional <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> who joined the ranks
